duties_responsibilities.duty: Handle customer calls and appointments for automotive dealerships.
Provide quality calls and maintain a positive and professional demeanor for the dealership.
Navigate dual-screen, multi-tab, and multiple platform programs while engaging in phone conversations with prospects.
Take notes during calls and summarize relevant points for the dealership.
Communicate effectively in English with proper grammar in both one-on-one and team environments.
Manage time effectively and multitask with discipline and patience.
